We support our brands with our strong supply and business platform. 



About ParklandBrandsManagementOur PromiseGovernanceAcquisitions











Parkland Brands
Parkland Fuel Corporation is North America’s local fuel company, operating through a family of brands delivering competitive petroleum products and serving communities through local operators who care. 



Bluewave Energy



Bluewave Energy is a Canadian petroleum distribution leader that specializes in delivering high-quality fuel, propane, lubricants and equipment to a growing number of businesses, industries and homeowners from coast to coast. Visit Website




Columbia Fuels



Columbia Fuels is a petroleum distribution leader that specializes in delivering high-quality fuel, lubricants and equipment to a growing number of businesses, industries and homeowners across British Columbia. Visit Website




Elbow River



Elbow River provides sales for all products on monthly or annual term supply contracts at a wide range of pricing alternatives from fixed prices to market differentials. Our market niche is shipping product via tank car by utilizing our large fleet of tank cars and our relationships with the railroads. Visit Website




Farstad Oil



In January 2013 Parkland Fuel Corporation entered the United States market with the purchase of SPF Energy Inc., the parent company of Farstad Oil Inc.  Farstad’s fleet of over 50 transports currently serves all of North Dakota and Montana, along with large portions of Minnesota, South Dakota and Wyoming. Farstad Oil supplies and distributes approximately one billion litres of gasoline and distillates, 80 million litres of propane and 10 million litres of lubricants annually. Visit Website




Fas Gas Plus



Customers have come to know Fas Gas Plus as a place they will receive better value and great service. As we seek to provide our customers with a great shopping experience you'll notice many Fas Gas Plus locations are brand new or have recently been fully renovated. Visit Website




Island Petroleum



Island Petroleum is a Canadian petroleum distribution leader that specializes in delivering high-quality fuel, lubricants and equipment to a growing number of businesses, industries and homeowners across Prince Edward Island. Visit Website




Les Pétroles Parkland



Les Pétroles Parkland, Parkland Fuel Corporation’s wholesale operations in Québec, customers can pick up or take delivery of petroleum products directly from the terminals. Visit Website




Pioneer Energy



Pioneer has been proudly serving Ontario motorists for more than five decades. We have worked hard at being the low-price leader in each of the markets we serve. We are committed to giving our customers the best possible value on each and every visit. Visit Website




Propane Nord-Ouest



Propane Nord-Ouest offers customers a turnkey service; from the sale, delivery and installation of appliances to the timely delivery of propane to keep their businesses operating and homes warm in northern Quebec and northeastern Ontario. Visit Website




Race Trac



Race Trac is a quick and convenient stop for the customer always on the move. Race Trac’s stations, which reach across Canada, are locally owned by independent dealers who offer products and services that often cater to the unique needs of the non-urban communities they operate in. Race Trac delivers exceptional value to customers. 



Sparlings



Sparlings is Ontario's second largest propane company and the oldest propane company in Canada. A fully integrated propane energy company, Sparlings provides reliable energy supply, appliances, equipment, and technical support to diverse markets in Central Canada. Visit Website




Superpumper



Superpumper, Inc. is a regional convenience store chain based in Minot, North Dakota. It was founded in 1983, and presently has 14 convenience store locations.  In 1996, Superpumper, Inc. merged with Farstad Oil, Inc. to form SPF Energy, Inc. Visit Website



















