Build a great career at a rapidly growing and evolving company. 







Working at ParklandIt is an exciting time to be a part of the Parkland team as we grow aggressively through the acquisition of both new customers and new companies. Our ongoing growth drives great opportunities for dynamic, ambitious and enthusiastic individuals, just like you, who are looking to define their future career by being part of a vibrant and growth oriented company today. 
Our main priority at Parkland is people. As an employee, you can expect a fair workplace, a professional work environment, competitive compensation, outstanding benefits, and a share in our success through the employee share purchase plan and our annual incentive plan.
Our employees also have the opportunity to develop their skills through continuous training and employee development. By helping our employees rise to new challenges, we give them the ability to further their careers while also furthering our mission to be the partner of choice to customers and suppliers.
If you’re up for a challenge and want to work with a dynamic and fun team, we want to hear from you! 


